snippet: The Red Bulls scored two second-half goals to defeat the expansion Atlanta United. Orlando City needed only Cyle Larin’s early header to beat N.Y.C.F.C....

headline.main: In Season Openers, the Red Bulls Rally and New York City F.C. Falls Short
headline.print_headline: Red Bulls Rally to Win Season Opener

lead_paragraph: The Red Bulls scored two second-half goals to defeat the expansion Atlanta United. Orlando City needed only Cyle Larin’s early header to beat N.Y.C.F.C.
